'''FINEX Management Services, Inc.''' is a privately held US [[Corporation]] headquartered in [[Tarrytown, New York]].<ref>[http://www.finexmanagement.com/program.asp]</ref>  FINEX provides systems for the automation of private medical practices, including analysis of non-medical business systems; [[Information Technology|IT]] systems with [[computer hardware|hardware]], billing, scheduling and EMR [[software]]; and human resource services including non-medical staff recruitment, training, supervision and management. The company employs more than fifty  billing, bookkeeping and medical practice management specialists, and serves medical practices billing over $250 million a year throughout the Greater New York Metropolitan region.

