l Aviv|access-date=3 April 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gutmanmuseum.co.il/%D7%AA%D7%A2%D7%A8%D7%95%D7%9B%D7%95%D7%AA/%D7%A7%D7%95%D7%93%D7%9E%D7%95%D7%AA/item/7-%D7%96%E2%80%99%D7%90%D7%A7-%D7%A7%D7%AA%D7%9E%D7%95%D7%A8-%D7%95%D7%94%D7%A2%D7%99%D7%9F-%D7%94%D7%A9%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%A9%D7%99%D7%AA-%D7%9C%D7%9E%D7%95%D7%AA-%D7%9C%D7%90%D7%98|script-title=he:ז׳אק קתמור והעין השלישית / למות לאט|trans-title=Jacques Katmor and The Third Eye / Slow Death|website=''[[Nahum Gutman Museum of Art]]''|language=Hebrew|access-date=3 April 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Barnea|first=Reut|date=9 February 2009|script-title=he:רטרוספקטיבה לז׳אק קתמור|trans-title=A Jacques Katmor Retrospective|url=http://www.calcalist.co.il/consumer/articles/0,7340,L-3561677,00.html|language=Hebrew|work=[[Calcalist]]|location=Tel Aviv|access-date=3 April 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|date=22 April 1965|script-title=he:ז׳. מורי־קתמור בגלריה "כץ"|trans-title=J. Mory-Katmor, at the "[[:he:גלריה לאמנות כ"ץ|Katz]]" Gallery|url=http://jpress.org.il/Olive/APA/NLI_Heb/SharedView.Article.aspx?parm=XqrnZgbJ1O4HIeDvAc4HdLLSQD7GAPjdS4nQf7x8j3kfQAvEI%2BPPoMqV2d99AYmuYw%3D%3D&mode=image&href=HRT%2f1965%2f04%2f22&page=5&rtl=true|language=Hebrew|work=[[Herut (newspaper)|Herut]]|location=Jerusalem|access-date=3 April 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|date=12 December 1969|script-title=he:מקרה גבר|last=Kesari|first=Uri|trans-title=A Man's Case|url=http://jpress.org.il/Olive/APA/NLI_Heb/SharedView.Article.aspx?parm=%2FZBcyTM2efPLRDKhPPbd2vtnlysU3sbl%2FKnO4wKYDrCdrx7PiunTqYGGXw%2FclFX7Yw%3D%3D&mode=image&href=MAR%2f1969%2f12%2f12&page=67&rtl=true|language=Hebrew|work=[[Maariv (newspaper)|Maariv]]|location=Tel Aviv|access-date=3 April 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|date=30 December 2011|script-title=he:מין, אירוטיקה ויהדות|trans-title=Sex, Eroticism, and, Judaism|last=Anderman|first=Nirit|url=http://www.haaretz.co.il/gallery/art/1.1604656|language=Hebrew|work=[[Haaretz]]|location=Tel Aviv|access-date=3 April 2017}}<